# WX ARENA — Project Rules for Zed AI

## Stack (NEVER deviate from this)
- Next.js 16 (App Router, TypeScript strict)
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Supabase SSR (@supabase/ssr) — server: getUser() NEVER getSession()
- Framer Motion for animations
- Zod for all validation
- Upstash Redis for rate limiting
- lucide-react for icons
- Named exports only (except page.tsx default exports)

## Next.js 16 Rules
- middleware.ts is RENAMED to proxy.ts — never create middleware.ts
- All params in pages/layouts are async: const { id } = await params
- Use "use cache" directive instead of PPR
- Turbopack is the default bundler — no webpack config needed

## Supabase Rules
- Server client: always import from @/lib/supabase/server
- Browser client: always import from @/lib/supabase/client
- NEVER call getSession() on the server — only getUser()
- All tables have RLS enabled

## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode — no 'any' types
- All components export named exports
- Use cn() from @/lib/utils/cn for className merging
- Keep components under 200 lines — split if larger
- No console.log in production code — use proper error handling

## File Structure
- App routes: app/(app)/ for protected pages
- App routes: app/(auth)/ for login/register
- API routes: app/api/
- Components: components/ui/ components/layout/ components/features/
- Lib: lib/supabase/ lib/security/ lib/validation/ lib/utils/

## Testing
- After each section: run `npm run type-check` — must pass with 0 errors
- Run `npm run dev` — must start without errors
- Check browser at localhost:3000


# WX ARENA — Agent Context

## What This Project Is
WX ARENA is a skill-based competitive gaming PWA for mobile-first markets in Africa, 
Southeast Asia, and Latin America. Games: eFootball, Dream League Soccer, Free Fire, 
PUBG Mobile, COD Mobile, EA FC 25.

## Current Build Phase
MVP — virtual points only (no real money). Phase 2 will add Paystack/Flutterwave.

## Key Decisions
- Next.js 16 + Supabase SSR (not Firebase, not Express)
- Vercel deployment
- PWA via @ducanh2912/next-pwa
- Virtual wallet (WX Points) — no real-money until licensing secured

## Do NOT
- Add Express.js or any separate backend server
- Use getSession() on the server
- Create middleware.ts (use proxy.ts instead)
- Use default exports in components (only in page.tsx files)
- Add purple gradients on white — this is a DARK app only

